TruckMuncher is Milwaukee's ultimate food truck hub! Whether you're searching for somewhere new to grab a bite or just want to see where your favorite truck is serving today, TruckMuncher will help you make the most of your lunch hour.

Own a food truck?
We've got you covered. Sign up at https://www.truckmuncher.com to get started and get your truck on the map!

Permissions
- Identity: We want you to always have the latest menus and truck locations, so we occasionally update in the background. This requires us to modify the TruckMuncher account on your device.
- Location: We use location to determine which trucks are closest to you. If you're a vendor, we also use it to report your truck location.
- Photos/Media/Files: We store data on your SD card if you have one so that your phone has more space for other apps.